<h1>What to Do</h1>
<p>Daytona Beach,FL is one of the best places in not only the state of Florida, but in the world. This beach landmark was founded in 1870, and has been known for it's family fun activities, such as our famous ferris wheel. Also, dine in at some our local restaurants, and be sure to step foot upon our beaches. Also, we are famous for the Daytona 500, every February, so purchase tickets whenever you like.</p>

